TRT: Teiresias Radiative Transfer v1.0 - (c) Ethan van Woerkom (2022)

 * Performs 1D/2D Relativistic Radiative Transfer on hydrodynamic  *
 * simulations from the Black Hole Accretion Code (O. Porth, 2017).*

   Takes arguments of form "-<key> <optional parameter to key>".

	 Arguments:  	 Description: 
	 -f <file>   	 Provide configuration file with additional
	             	 arguments.
	 --version   	 Display TRT version.
	 -h / --help 	 Display this help message.

	 Notes:

 * This software has been released under the GNU LGPL 3.0 license. *
